'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 9''' is the ninth issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints, published on [[April 5]], [[1978]].

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 5|''Star Wars'' (1977) 5]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 1|Man-Gods from Beyond the Stars]]" {{C|Part 4}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 4|The Sword in the Star!: Stave 1: Alas, the Seeds of Man!]]" {{C|Part 5}}

*A competition to win one of fifty ''Star Wars'' rub-down transfers from Letraset. To enter, readers must answer six ''Star War''s related fill-in-the-blank statements.

